OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain will clear south
OL,6,Fthrough the morning. A fine and
OL,7,Fsettled day thereafter with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine, although East Anglia may see
OL,9,Finfrequent coastal showers. Feeling
OL,10,Fcool in brisk northerly winds,
OL,11,Fparticularly along coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear overnight skies will
OL,14,Fallow temperatures to fall away
OL,15,Fquickly, with a rural frost forming.
OL,16,FRemaining breezy during the evening,
OL,17,Fespecially along coasts, before winds
OL,18,Ffalling light overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
