OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA sunny but cold start, with
OL,6,Fcloud increasing ahead of a band of
OL,7,Fpatchy rain moving south during the
OL,8,Fearly afternoon, clearing into the
OL,9,Fevening. Winds strengthening through
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FFrequent blustery showers on Wednesday
OL,14,Fand Thursday, occasionally heavy with
OL,15,Fa risk of thunder. Friday cloudy and
OL,16,Fmostly dry, with some bright or sunny
OL,17,Fspells. Feeling rather cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
